+## WHY
+We have the Scoreboard and the Referee. Now we need the AI Architect to actually write the new trading strategies.
+
+## WHAT
+
+Create scripts/ai_propose.py:
+
+This script must connect to the DeepSeek API (use the DEEPSEEK_API_KEY from the environment).
+
+It reads the code in user_data/strategies/blocks/rsi_simple.py and macd_simple.py as examples.
+
+Task: For the outsider slots in league.json, ask the AI to invent a completely new Python file in user_data/strategies/blocks/ with unique logic (e.g., using Volume or Bollinger Bands).
+
+Task: For the promising slots, ask the AI to tweak the existing champion code to make it safer.
+
+Safety: Use ast.parse to make sure the AI didn't write "broken" Python code. If it's broken, don't save it.
+
+## HOW
+
+Use the requests library to talk to https://api.deepseek.com/v1/chat/completions.
+
+Use scripts/paths.py for all file saving.
+
+Ensure the new blocks are added to the active_blocks list in a temporary dna.json for testing.
+
+

